          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-3-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 550ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[775ml]<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[150ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>milk </strong>– this is your <strong>creamy</strong> <strong>vegetable stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-4-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-4-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
