          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the leek has softened, add 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>flour</strong> and cook for 30 secs or until fragrant</p><p>Add the<strong> creamy vegetable stock </strong>and <strong>chopped potatoes</strong> and cook for 15-18 min or until the potatoes are almost fork-tender</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-5-x700.jpg",
