          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1454.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the haddock and potatoes are cooking, chop your <strong>chives</strong> finely</p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Once everything is done, add the <strong>grated cheddar cheese</strong> to the pot and gently stir everything together – this is your<strong> one-pot cheesy haddock & leek chowder</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
